# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# Syntax: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# The first matching rule wins — order matters.

# Root → default locale. Astro emits a 2-second meta-refresh stub at /,
# but a proper 301 is faster, better for SEO (passes canonical signal),
# and survives edge caches. Phase 3 will add per-Accept-Language
# negotiation; for Phase 0 (DE-only) a static redirect is correct.
/ /de/ 301
